## Required Follow-Up

- Create worktrees only after `.vibeos/worktree-scopes.json` is committed on the base branch.
- Open one agent session per worktree.
- Rebase remaining worktrees after every merge to main.
- Keep `FLOW-INTEGRITY.md` or equivalent evidence current as implementation changes.
- Keep `SYSTEM-INVARIANTS.md` or equivalent evidence current as implementation changes.
- Keep `DEPENDENCY-INTELLIGENCE.md` or equivalent evidence current as dependency and runtime decisions change.
- Keep `DELIVERY-INFRASTRUCTURE.md` or equivalent evidence current as CI/CD, deployment, observability, smoke checks, rollback, and runbooks change.
- Run `comp_gauntlet` before final demo or handoff.
